{"tid":523985,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【私影少女被殺】被告不欲案件於猴年開審 小欖醫生：被告適合答辯","createTime":"2018-01-09T06:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T07:14:38.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"432fd5f73e9f6b9e8354187dd6ac7bc3cf0ea2c0","tid":523985,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180109/large/1515478426_85c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180109%2Flarge%2F1515478426_85c9.jpg&h=51b78d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180109/large/1515478464_638c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180109%2Flarge%2F1515478464_638c.jpg&h=43cedcc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已婚無業漢涉虐殺15歲私影少女案，陪審團須決定被告是否適合答辯。控方今傳召小欖精神科醫生陳炤佑作供。陳表示被告曾提及神曾就揀選陪審團給他指示，例如陪審員的性別需要是「男男女男男女」，但陳亦認為此非被告幻覺，只是他有錯覺以為這樣較好，又透露被告一向對審訊有其意見，例如被告基於風水原因不想案件在猴年開審等，因此他對被告關於陪審團性別有意見並不感驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n醫生陳炤佑從2014年開始接見被告劉璋輝（37歲），至今超過50次，最後一次是應法庭要求於上週在法院大樓接見被告。根據陳撰寫的精神報告，他指被告於2017年10月前並沒有精神病，只是有自閉症的徵狀，但並非嚴重，如被告性格悲觀、交友方面內向及沒有安全感；直到去年10月被告突然患有急性精神病，性情變得暴躁，陳遂處方藥物予被告，及後被告的情況已有改善，變得冷靜克制。<br />\n<br />\n陳炤佑指被告清楚理解控罪及審訊時發生的事情，雖然被告曾向陳表示有幻聽，聽到神及妻子、女性友人的聲音，但陳仍認為被告並非同一時間聽到兩把聲音，所以不會影響被告應訊時的專注力，認為被告適合答辯。"},{"pid":"786cfff12e64a62e0f43676aebc679b1955ab34f","tid":523985,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:34:51.000Z","msg":"扮傻呀啦，答辯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ff031bf6b620fd0773b68ab21879a0f0933c65","tid":523985,"uid":6097,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"以為鳩噏幾句九唔撘八就可以扮傻博小欖<br />\n你係醒就唔會搞到今日田地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蠢得都幾均勻 正正經經答辯啦木咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0f433d8605dae793e316c943db7eb35d31bc2d","tid":523985,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"當人on9"},{"pid":"9d7d086473477403284f9acd8c74b1fb37d92368","tid":523985,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:43:37.000Z","msg":"但陳仍認為被告並非同一時間聽到兩把聲音，所以不會影響被告應訊時的專注力，認為被告適合答辯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68ddcc3f8812178b515fc38cb5a7e54ac5c48d5","tid":523985,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:47:56.000Z","msg":"可能今次條友要即場除褲痾完再食先有用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974b05d0163804fb45c8b47e5c0b1f6be0216360","tid":523985,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:03:55.000Z","msg":"試下上到庭跳結他他舞睇下有無幫助啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fdb1075729c25f5bae3f0552b6567365b84a47","tid":523985,"uid":94774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"入面實大把人招呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4749d09b6cb733fa2dbbf8d04f570303fdbbdc2","tid":523985,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b68ddcc3f8812178b515fc38cb5a7e54ac5c48d5","tid":523985,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:47:56.000Z","msg":"可能今次條友要即場除褲痾完再食先有用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"睇怕要學泡菜<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">韓裔男大鬧布吉機場 剝光豬向人掟屎</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180109/57683987\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F57683987&d=xX77hroXdMzR4jOVmCMNZQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=b8ea6063\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180109%2F57683987&h=d060bb88\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180109/57683987</a><br />\n<br />\n一名27歲美籍韓裔男子在泰國布吉國際機場候機室裸體示眾，更手執自己的糞便扔向執法人員。男子被捕後向警方承認，他是因為服食過量壯陽藥威爾鋼（俗稱「偉哥」）才失去理智。<br />\n<br />\n來自紐約、持有美國護照的崔姓男子（Steve Cho）上周四在布吉機場等待飛往南韓仁川，期間突然脫去身上衣物在候機室內行走，在場的乘客嚇得目瞪口呆。機場職員立即走上前嘗試阻止男子，但對方並未冷靜下來，更一度向職員扔自己的糞便。<br />\n<br />\n機場職員其後出動6名保安人員，將男子帶離候機室並成功將他制服。男子接受警方問話時坦承，自己是因服食過量壯陽藥而失去理智。他承認鬧事，並同意為他造成的財物損失賠償。不過，當局決定取消他的登機資格，並安排他到當地醫院接受精神檢查。<br />\n<br />\n一名目擊者憶述事件時形容：「那是我在機場看過最可怕及噁心的事。機場職員當時嘗時使他冷靜下來，並嘗試和他對話，但他無視了他們。」"},{"pid":"9c04bed919fc4b89ed18653f6b6671e70f3116c6","tid":523985,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">無業漢稱案發時聽到「血祭」　小欖精神科醫生：被告沒精神病</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180109/s00001/1515478536602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180109%2Fs00001%2F1515478536602&d=xX77hroXdMzR4jOVmCMNZQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=f590b13a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180109%2Fs00001%2F1515478536602&h=6885a94c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180109/s00001/1515478536602</a><br />\n<br />\n無業漢3年前相約15歲少女到其寓所「私影」，涉嫌侵犯及殺害她，案件今續審。辯方早前稱被告精神狀况有變，不適合繼續審訊，並傳召精神科醫生作供。控方今傳召無業漢於小欖的主診精神科醫生作供，他指對方有妄想症徵狀，但認為他無精神病，故適合答辯。<br />\n<br />\n被告劉璋輝（37歲），被控於2014年12月8日謀殺當時15歲的郭惠明，他早前否認一項謀殺罪，但表示願意承認誤殺，惟不獲控方接納。辯方上周指出，被告的精神狀况有變，法庭決定交由陪審團決定被告是否可繼續審訊。<br />\n<br />\n控方今傳召精神科醫生陳炤佑作供，自被告被捕後，他曾先後57次與被告會面。陳表示，被告的人格評估顯示他缺乏安全感、容易對事物敏感，並會抽離現實，這些均為妄想症的病徵。<br />\n<br />\n陳指出，被告曾向他表示聽到來自上帝的聲音，但認為被告並無受到聲音騷擾致分心，因被告交談時說話清晰有條理，不似被干擾。陳又指，被告能清楚表達謀殺罪涉及有意圖和明知等元素，而誤殺則沒有，故認為他能理解控罪，明白法庭程序。<br />\n<br />\n至於被告曾稱案發時聽到「血祭」一詞，陳透露此是被告於前年9月才首次提及，認為如被告真有如此不正常表現，他理應感到很真實，會在案發翌日與警方的錄影會面中提及。"},{"pid":"4354065a1d2dc7c36a1c862a3f8f1e1f64f7d924","tid":523985,"uid":738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:14:38.000Z","msg":"弱鳩智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}